data.description: Beautiful view of the city with this well kept 4 bedroom split level. This home features include a grand brick fireplace, vaulted ceiling with a beam, balcony with a view, large deck and even a salt water pool! Kitchen includes updated appliances, granite counter tops, and an open dining room. Three bedrooms and a full bathroom are located upstairs including a master with an attached bathroom. New Pergo flooring and carpeting is upstairs. Downstairs you will find a spacious family room with a pellet stove, laundry room/bathroom, and another bedroom. Plenty of convenient storage is included in the home and double car garage. The roof and windows are newer.The location is private with only one close neighbor and very safe with a security system. You will love the peaceful woods right in your backyard along with plenty of room to play and garden. This home is perfect for a family and entertaining.
data.whatILove: A beautiful view, grand architectural features, and a pool with a grand deck really set this home apart others.
